# IPC Debugger Simulation

Interactive educational website for visualizing Inter-Process Communication mechanisms in Operating Systems.

## Live Demo
Open `index.html` in your browser to start exploring!

## Features
- 🔗 Pipes Simulator
- 📬 Message Queue Simulator  
- 🧠 Shared Memory Simulator
- 🌓 Dark Mode Support
- 📱 Fully Responsive
